        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/17/1",
        "text": [
          " قَالَ رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : «إِذَا غَابَ اَلْقُرْصُ أَفْطَرَ اَلصَّائِمُ وَ دَخَلَ وَقْتُ اَلصَّلاَةِ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.1932 - Amru ibn Shimr narrated from Jabir, from Abu Ja'far (as), who said that the Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace be upon him and his family) said:\n\"When the disk of the sun disappears, the fasting person may break their fast, and the time for prayer begins.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 362,
        "local_index": 2,
        "narrator_chain": {
          "parts": [
